---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Marcos Natã Santos" description="A bit about me, my background, and what I'm up to.">
  <section class="about">
    <div class="about-header">
      <img src="/profile.jpeg" alt="Marcos Natã Santos" class="about-photo" width="120" height="120" />
      <div>
        <h1>About me</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Software engineer, AI enthusiast, from Brazil.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        Hey! I'm Marcos. I'm a software engineer with over 10 years
        of experience building things for the web. These days I spend most of my time
        working with AI and leading engineering teams.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm currently leading teams building an agent platform for financial and professional services. Before that,
        I built AI tools to help real estate agents work smarter.
      </p>

      <p>
        Over the years I've worked across the full stack -- front-end, back-end, DevOps,
        mobile apps, ERP systems -- you name it. I've been a tech lead, a co-founder, and
        even a professor teaching AI to developers. I like wearing different hats.
      </p>

      <h2>This blog</h2>

      <p>
        This is my little corner of the internet where I write about software, AI, and
        whatever else is on my mind. Nothing too formal -- just sharing things I find
        interesting or useful.
      </p>

      <div class="links">
        <a href="https://github.com/marcosnataqs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <span class="separator">/</span>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/marcosnataqs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        <span class="separator">/</span>
        <a href="https://x.com/marcosnataqs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a>
        <span class="separator">/</span>
        <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .about-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-content strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .links {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .separator {
    margin: 0 0.35rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .about-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .about-photo {
      width: 90px;
      height: 90px;
    }
  }
</style>
